          <a
            href="https://devignition.com/"
            target="_blank">Write Once, Stream Everywhere: Transforming Your Data into Events</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="event-name">
          <a href="https://devignition.com/" target="_blank">DevIgnition</a>
        </div>
        <span class="date">Nov 7, 2024 in Alexandria, Virginia</span>
